                              'Angoes' 2.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Angoes' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} which is played on an 8 by 8 tile
board, the idea is to align 3 or more of the coloured angles so
they are pointing in the same direction. The catch is that each
angle can only point in 2 directions: either left and right or up
and down.

  Have fun!

